plot: Melissa tries to keep Christmas traditions alive, despite living in a rental home, while Dina feels more alone than ever as her daughter Lexi applies for college. Amber, on the other hand, isn't ready to let go of her precious children just yet and becomes consumed with home safety, while Teresa Aprea decides it's time for her son, Giovanni, to join the family empire - interning at his father's restaurant. Meanwhile, Teresa Giudice's legal woes still hang heavy over her family's head as she struggles to keep things normal for her girls and vows to Joe that this will not be their last Christmas together.—Anonymous
